----[ Purpose

	This plugin Display all device in a Google map.

----[ Installation

	To install the plugin, please refer to the Plugin Installation Documentation
	You need to install php-xml extension https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14395239/class-domdocument-not-found

----[ Possible Bugs?
   

----[ Future Changes

	Got any ideas or complaints, please e-mail me!
	Add the option of OpenStreetMap

----[ Changelog
	0.33 The snmp location format change to include GPS value in the following 
         format: Country;City;Street_Building;Floor;Room;Rack;RU;Lat;Long

	0.34 Minor bug correction, and search baes on description instead of hostname/ip address
	0.35 Added the option to geocode only one device at time
	0.36 Added the option to define the center of the map from the settings (if no center is given Greenwich is used,
		 and add openstreetmap function
	
	
